query:
SELECT 
	Users.UserName 
	, Teams.TeamName

	,COUNT(Quotes.Quote_ID) AS n_f3_records
	, SUM(CASE WHEN Quotes.Type LIKE '%Quote%' AND Quotes.Status LIKE '%Open%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS n_open_quotes
	, ISNULL(SUM(CASE WHEN Quotes.Type LIKE '%Quote%' THEN ForecastAmount ELSE 0 END), 0) AS fcst_smnt

FROM Users 
	LEFT OUTER JOIN Teams ON Teams.Team_ID = Users.Team_ID AND Teams.Organization_ID = 1
	LEFT OUTER JOIN Quotes ON Quotes.User_ID = Users.User_ID AND Quotes.Organization_ID = 1

WHERE (1=1)
	AND Users.Organization_ID = 1
	AND (Quotes.CreateDate = '2016-11-30' OR Quotes.ModDate = '2016-11-30')

GROUP BY UserName, TeamName
